* v0.0.8

- 4 new models imported
  (ripi, ai, cnai, cnbi), check ChangeLog

- Remove pi from cosmopar as it is already defined in infprec

- Fix typos in lmi man

- Adding cnai_x_potzero() function in cnaisr

- Some significant changes in cnbi, coded new functions and added an
  efold test in the trajectory to get enough efolds of inflation. The
  new functions are:
      cnbi_x_potzero, cnbi_x_potinfty, cnbi_x_epsoneunity,
      cnbi_epsilon_one_min, cnbi_x_epsonemin
  and removed cnbi_xend_max.

- Adding the corresponding descriptions in the man

